2026-05-12T21:39:13.5281335Z 22    <!--
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5281910Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5282974Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5283676Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5284596Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5285428Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5286465Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5287299Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T21:39:13.5288137Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
